msgstr "%1 suena en el grupo"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:2997
msgid "Whether this speaker plays in the group — untick to leave it out without disconnecting it. Remembered for the device."
msgstr "Si este altavoz suena en el grupo — desmárcalo para dejarlo fuera sin desconectarlo. Se recuerda para el dispositivo."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3010
msgid "Balance of %1"
msgstr "Balance de %1"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qml:3019
msgid "This speaker's share of the volume — the balance follows every master move and is remembered for the device."
msgstr "La parte de este altavoz en el volumen: el balance sigue cada movimiento del control maestro y se recuerda para el dispositivo."

