msgstr "pactl rechazó crear la salida combinada."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:335
msgid "The Bluetooth speaker trails by %1 ms, and every speaker's loudness was matched at the microphone — all set and remembered."
msgstr "El altavoz Bluetooth va %1 ms por detrás, y el volumen de todos los altavoces se igualó en el micrófono — todo ajustado y recordado."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:336
msgid "The Bluetooth speaker trails by %1 ms — the delay is set and remembered for this device."
msgstr "El altavoz Bluetooth se retrasa %1 ms — el retardo queda ajustado y recordado para este dispositivo."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:338
msgid "Balance levels set earlier were replaced by the measured ones."
msgstr "Los niveles de balance ajustados antes se sustituyeron por los medidos."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:346
msgid "The microphone clipped on %1 — that balance was left unchanged; lower the speaker's volume and calibrate again."
msgstr "El micrófono saturó con %1 — ese balance quedó sin cambios; baja el volumen del altavoz y calibra de nuevo."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:347
msgid "Speakers calibrated"
msgstr "Altavoces calibrados"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:359
msgid "Calibration did not succeed"
msgstr "La calibración no tuvo éxito"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:360
msgid "Make sure the microphone is not covered and both speakers can be heard, then try again."
msgstr "Asegúrate de que el micrófono no esté tapado y de que se oigan ambos altavoces, luego inténtalo de nuevo."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:403
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:419
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:434
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:444
#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:457
msgid "Sync check"
msgstr "Comprobación de sincronización"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:404
msgid "The speakers were %1 ms apart — adjusted from the measurement, checking once more."
msgstr "Los altavoces estaban a %1 ms de diferencia — ajustado según la medición, comprobando una vez más."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:420
msgid "A speaker's route was stuck %1 ms behind — flushed it, checking once more."
msgstr "La ruta de un altavoz estaba atascada %1 ms — se vació, comprobando una vez más."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:435
msgid "The room was not quiet enough to verify — pause other audio and calibrate once more."
msgstr "La sala no estaba lo bastante en silencio para verificar — pausa el resto del audio y calibra otra vez."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:445
msgid "Could not hear %1 during the check — the speaker may be muted or off. The calibration was kept."
msgstr "No se oyó %1 durante la comprobación — el altavoz puede estar silenciado o apagado. La calibración se conservó."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:453
msgid "Sync verified"
msgstr "Sincronización verificada"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:454
msgid "Every speaker arrives within %1 ms at the microphone — in step to the ear."
msgstr "Cada altavoz llega al micrófono en un margen de %1 ms — al oído, en perfecta sincronía."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:458
msgid "The speakers still arrive %1 ms apart. Calibrate once more, or nudge the delay slider."
msgstr "Los altavoces aún llegan con %1 ms de diferencia. Calibra otra vez o ajusta el deslizador de retardo."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:1046
msgid "All local outputs (On Air)"
msgstr "Todas las salidas locales (On Air)"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:1500
msgid "%1 did not join the sync"
msgstr "%1 no se unió a la sincronización"

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:1502
msgid "The speaker is connected but could not be pulled into the group — switch the sync off and on to rebuild it."
msgstr "El altavoz está conectado, pero no se pudo incorporar al grupo — apaga y vuelve a encender la sincronización."

#: /home/egon/Projects/on-air-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/SyncEngine.qml:1503
msgid "The speaker is connected but its audio output never appeared — switch the speaker off and on, then connect it again."
msgstr "El altavoz está conectado, pero su salida de audio nunca apareció — apaga y enciende el altavoz y vuelve a conectarlo."

